is a friend of my brother's.

795
01:01:47,078 --> 01:01:50,122
You have a beautiful everything.

796
01:01:52,166 --> 01:01:53,375
Yes, he does.

797
01:01:53,459 --> 01:01:54,835
Yes, I do.

798
01:01:54,919 --> 01:01:57,295
- I'm gonna kiss Nicki good night.
