01:02:52,602 --> 01:02:53,852
How are you, brother?

800
01:02:53,936 --> 01:02:57,689
Oh, you know,
still the resident family fuck up.

801
01:02:58,524 --> 01:03:02,778
- Yeah, well, I guess someone has to do it.
